Hey, person who got into ask riot asking for Kalista buffs.


{{sticker:slayer-jinx-wink}} 

But for real, is this your idea of a buff? a bug fix and a mana refund, a good Kalista player doesn't even need the "permanent stacking" because they ALWAYS get their cooldowns back. seriously, idk how long ago that ask riot was but its been around 2 months.
 holy mother of anticlimactic bull shit. if you wanna buff Kalista, remove the BS parts of her passive, like the fact that her auto attacks can fucking miss, and that her auto attacks only deal %90 of AD {{item:3070}} ... really? it makes no sense. she has NO late-game b/c of that last one, and there are two bushes in the bot lane... fuck i'm pissed idk if ill be playing much more LoL 

 {{sticker:zombie-brand-facepalm}} 

Overwatch is better anyways.
